      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Richard Pennycook is the lead non-executive board member of the Department for Education. He joined in October 2017.</p>

<p>He is chair of Howdens Joinery, Fenwick and the Hut Group, and chair of the British Retail Consortium.</p>

<p>Between March 2014 and February 2017 he was Chief Executive of the Co-operative Group.</p>

</div>
      </section>

